A farmer and his son live on a farm, they have only one horse to pull the
plow. One day, the horse runs away, and the neighbors come over and say What
terrible news!, the farmer says Good news, or bad news? The next day, the
horse returns, and with him, come an entire herd of feral horses! The
neighbors come back and say What great news!, the farmer says, Good new, or
bad news? The next day, while trying to tame one of the new horses, the
farmers' son falls and breaks his leg. The neighbors say What terrible 
news!, Good news, or bad news? The next day, the army visits to conscript
all able-bodied men to go to war, the farmers' son is spared, because of his 
broken leg. What good news!, Good news, or bad news?
